  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening of Teacher&apos;s Training, Evaluation and Recognition</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Objective of the Project is to strengthen the development of teachers&apos; professional capabilities both in initial and in-service training to improve training and the learning achievements of students, and other actions in relation to the implementation of Law 29944, within the framework of teachers&apos; re-valuing policy. The Project has established 4 expected results, which are based on a set of activities oriented to the strengthening of capabilities for the implementation of teacher initial training, in-service training, evaluation, teacher recognition and well-being promotion policies, implementation of the National Curriculum, and strategic planning.</narrative>
  </description>
